== 評價 ==
該片整體而言獲得了積極的評價。IGN給了總比分8.8/10，稱這是一個「偉大的現代起源故事，其動作和幽默會贏得您的青睞」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/02/08/justice-league-war-blu-ray-review |title=IGN: Justice League: War Blu-Ray Review |publisher=Feeds.ign.com |date=2014-02-07 |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207193013/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/02/08/justice-league-war-blu-ray-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[CraveOnline|CraveOnline]]給了9/10這樣的分數<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.craveonline.com/comics/reviews/635549-review-justice-league-war |title=Review: Justice League: War |publisher=craveonline.com |date=2014-02-16 |accessdate=2014-01-24 |archive-date=2014-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915061319/http://www.craveonline.com/comics/reviews/635549-review-justice-league-war |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[IMDb|IMDb]]在10條評論中給了有7.2的總分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3060952/ |title=IGN: Justice League: War (Video 2014) |publisher=imdb.com |date=2014-02-16 |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222114336/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3060952/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Variety|Variety]]的布賴恩·洛瑞認為此部的品質沒有到達以往[[DC宇宙動畫原創電影|DC動畫電影]]的水準，稱「相互作用所所佔的時間，但最終證明過於瘋狂和混亂，提供超過幾個修正主義的驚險刺激」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/blu-ray-review-justice-league-war-1201083751/ |title="Justice League: War" Blue-Ray Review |publisher=variety.com |date=2014-02-03 |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206103644/https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/blu-ray-review-justice-league-war-1201083751/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Nerdist_Industries|Nerdist Industries]]的艾里克·迪亞茲對這片給了C，得出的結論是：「如果這些都是DC的英雄，我們將看到的唯一在動畫版本中可預見的未來，那麼他們將不得不從我們所看到的正義聯盟：戰爭來改善」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nerdist.com/2014/02/review-justice-league-war/ |title=review: JUSTICE LEAGUE: WAR |publisher=nerdist.com |date=2014-02-16 |accessdate=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312063536/http://www.nerdist.com/2014/02/review-justice-league-war/ |archive-date=2014-03-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

